{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56735, "create_time": 1648001757, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "“中国人丝毫不在乎流感病毒的传播，每年冬天都有大量农村老人死于H1N1感染，中国人归结为“命”、“熬不过冬天”。”", "timestamp": 1648001757}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56736, "create_time": 1648002022, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 1, "text": "[tmp]\n农村老人都有各种慢性病或癌症。冬天确实死亡率高但也都是七八十岁了", "timestamp": 1648002022}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56740, "create_time": 1648002328, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 其实美国的一百万新冠死亡病例中，也大多数都是有基础病的老年人", "timestamp": 1648002328}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56741, "create_time": 1648002416, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 1, "text": "[tmp]\nRe 洞主: 给个年龄比例，不要说大多数", "timestamp": 1648002416}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56742, "create_time": 1648002537, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 1, "text": "[tmp]\n农村里好几个村子几千人才有一个小诊所几张床位。", "timestamp": 1648002537}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56744, "create_time": 1648002671, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\n如果到时候全民感染了，难道医院可以规定只接受青年患者拒绝接受老年患者让他们等死吗", "timestamp": 1648002671}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56746, "create_time": 1648002871, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 75岁以上占52%，65岁以上占75.1%，50岁以上占91%。[来源：美国疾控中心](https://covid.cdc.gov/covid-data-tracker/#demographics)\n\n![](https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2022/03/bbe719ececa4b872.png)", "timestamp": 1648002871}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56749, "create_time": 1648003272, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "随着年龄上升，感染新冠的概率没有升高，但住院、死亡的概率都在指数上升。[来源：美国疾控中心](https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/covid-data/investigations-discovery/hospitalization-death-by-age.html)\n![](https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2022/03/d4e2e243a83373f5.png)", "timestamp": 1648003272}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56766, "create_time": 1648004974, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 难道医院可以规定因为疫情防控拒绝接受其他患者让他们等死吗（答案是，真的可以）", "timestamp": 1648004974}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56769, "create_time": 1648005230, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 跟疫情没关系，癌症晚期也不接收", "timestamp": 1648005230}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56771, "create_time": 1648005327, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 我指的是西安孕妇、吉林女童这样的事件，当然跟疫情有关系", "timestamp": 1648005327}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56776, "create_time": 1648005561, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 有没有可能放开之后更没他们看病的机会", "timestamp": 1648005561}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56778, "create_time": 1648005625, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 流感让他们没看病的机会了吗？", "timestamp": 1648005625}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56787, "create_time": 1648005797, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 为什么会有医疗挤兑，各种渲染恐慌的宣传是个很重要的原因。香港这一波死亡率高，原因之一就是轻症把医院挤满了，重症的住不上院。\n>\n如果要放开的话，我认为肯定需要先加强宣传，告诉大家Omicron只是大号流感。", "timestamp": 1648005797}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56788, "create_time": 1648005861, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以不能急啊，只能一步步来", "timestamp": 1648005861}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56811, "create_time": 1648007622, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "别说农村。城里的老人出去旅游一趟得流感然后去世的也非常多。", "timestamp": 1648007622}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 56818, "create_time": 1648007863, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "是这样的，突然一病（可能就是小病），然后子女不送大医院，就没了", "timestamp": 1648007863}], "create_time": 1648001677, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1648007863, "likenum": 9, "n_attentions": 9, "n_comments": 17, "pid": 20887, "poll": null, "reply": 17, "text": ">在农村的都知道，村里老人容易“冬天一场大病没熬过去，去世了好几位”。[出处](https://www.zhihu.com/answer/2395675859)\n\n我自己不是在农村长大的。有没有了解情况的同学说说，真的是这样吗？\n\n#20750", "timestamp": 1648001677}}